### Booking State Machine — Manual Test Scenarios
### Requires VS Code REST Client extension or JetBrains HTTP Client
### Base URL: https://localhost:5001

@base = https://localhost:5001
@processKey = booking-demo-001
@corr = {{$guid}}

### ── Scenario 1: Happy path ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Step 0 — Create process
POST {{base}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "processKey": "{{processKey}}",
  "correlationId": "corr-001"
}

###

# Step 1 — Reserve room
POST {{base}}/api/bookings/{{processKey}}/transitions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "processKey": "{{processKey}}",
  "event": "ReserveRoom",
  "idempotencyKey": "ikey-001",
  "correlationId": "corr-001",
  "simulateFailure": false
}

###

# Step 2 — Send notification
POST {{base}}/api/bookings/{{processKey}}/transitions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "processKey": "{{processKey}}",
  "event": "SendNotification",
  "idempotencyKey": "ikey-002",
  "correlationId": "corr-001",
  "simulateFailure": false
}

###

# Step 3 — Confirm
POST {{base}}/api/bookings/{{processKey}}/transitions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "processKey": "{{processKey}}",
  "event": "Confirm",
  "idempotencyKey": "ikey-003",
  "correlationId": "corr-001",
  "simulateFailure": false
}

###

# Check state
GET {{base}}/api/bookings/{{processKey}}

###

### ── Scenario 2: Idempotency — send same key twice ──────────────────────────

POST {{base}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "processKey": "booking-idem-001",
  "correlationId": "corr-idem"
}

###

POST {{base}}/api/bookings/booking-idem-001/transitions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "processKey": "booking-idem-001",
  "event": "ReserveRoom",
  "idempotencyKey": "FIXED-KEY-XYZ",
  "correlationId": "corr-idem",
  "simulateFailure": false
}

###

# Send SAME idempotency key again — state must NOT change
POST {{base}}/api/bookings/booking-idem-001/transitions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "processKey": "booking-idem-001",
  "event": "ReserveRoom",
  "idempotencyKey": "FIXED-KEY-XYZ",
  "correlationId": "corr-idem",
  "simulateFailure": false
}

###

### ── Scenario 3: Compensation — fail on SendNotification ────────────────────

POST {{base}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "processKey": "booking-comp-001",
  "correlationId": "corr-comp"
}

###

POST {{base}}/api/bookings/booking-comp-001/transitions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "processKey": "booking-comp-001",
  "event": "ReserveRoom",
  "idempotencyKey": "comp-ikey-001",
  "correlationId": "corr-comp",
  "simulateFailure": false
}

###

# This step will fail → compensation runs automatically
POST {{base}}/api/bookings/booking-comp-001/transitions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "processKey": "booking-comp-001",
  "event": "SendNotification",
  "idempotencyKey": "comp-ikey-002",
  "correlationId": "corr-comp",
  "simulateFailure": true
}

###

# Check — state should be Cancelled
GET {{base}}/api/bookings/booking-comp-001

###

### ── Scenario 4: Invalid transition (out of order) ─────────────────────────

POST {{base}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "processKey": "booking-invalid-001",
  "correlationId": "corr-inv"
}

###

# Try to Confirm directly from Created → expect 422
POST {{base}}/api/bookings/booking-invalid-001/transitions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "processKey": "booking-invalid-001",
  "event": "Confirm",
  "idempotencyKey": "inv-ikey-001",
  "correlationId": "corr-inv",
  "simulateFailure": false
}

###

### ── Health & Metrics ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

GET {{base}}/health/live

###

GET {{base}}/health/ready

###

GET {{base}}/metrics

###

GET {{base}}/api/bookings
